{"pageNumber":450,"juzNumber":23,"verses":[{"key":"37:103","surahNumber":37,"ayahNumber":103,"juzNumber":23,"pageNumber":450,"arabicText":"فَلَمَّآ أَسْلَمَا وَتَلَّهُۥ لِلْجَبِينِ","translationText":"And when they had both submitted and he put him down upon his forehead,"},{"key":"37:104","surahNumber":37,"ayahNumber":104,"juzNumber":23,"pageNumber":450,"arabicText":"وَنَٰدَيْنَٰهُ أَن يَٰٓإِبْرَٰهِيمُ","translationText":"We called to him, \"O Abraham,"},{"key":"37:105","surahNumber":37,"ayahNumber":105,"juzNumber":23,"pageNumber":450,"arabicText":"قَدْ صَدَّقْتَ ٱلرُّءْيَآ ۚ إِنَّا كَذَٰلِكَ نَجْزِى ٱلْمُحْسِنِينَ","translationText":"You have fulfilled the vision.\" Indeed, We thus reward the doers of good."},{"key":"37:106","surahNumber":37,"ayahNumber":106,"juzNumber":23,"pageNumber":450,"arabicText":"إِنَّ هَٰذَا لَهُوَ ٱلْبَلَٰٓؤُا۟ ٱلْمُبِينُ","translationText":"Indeed, this was the clear trial."},{"key":"37:107","surahNumber":37,"ayahNumber":107,"juzNumber":23,"pageNumber":450,"arabicText":"وَفَدَيْنَٰهُ بِذِبْحٍ عَظِيمٍۢ","translationText":"And We ransomed him with a great sacrifice,"},{"key":"37:108","surahNumber":37,"ayahNumber":108,"juzNumber":23,"pageNumber":450,"arabicText":"وَتَرَكْنَا عَلَيْهِ فِى ٱلْءَاخِرِينَ","translationText":"And We left for him [favorable mention] among later generations:"},{"key":"37:109","surahNumber":37,"ayahNumber":109,"juzNumber":23,"pageNumber":450,"arabicText":"سَلَٰمٌ عَلَىٰٓ إِبْرَٰهِيمَ","translationText":"\"Peace upon Abraham.\""},{"key":"37:110","surahNumber":37,"ayahNumber":110,"juzNumber":23,"pageNumber":450,"arabicText":"كَذَٰلِكَ نَجْزِى ٱلْمُحْسِنِينَ","translationText":"Indeed, We thus reward the doers of good."},{"key":"37:111","surahNumber":37,"ayahNumber":111,"juzNumber":23,"pageNumber":450,"arabicText":"إِنَّهُۥ مِنْ عِبَادِنَا ٱلْمُؤْمِنِينَ","translationText":"Indeed, he was of Our believing servants."},{"key":"37:112","surahNumber":37,"ayahNumber":112,"juzNumber":23,"pageNumber":450,"arabicText":"وَبَشَّرْنَٰهُ بِإِسْحَٰقَ نَبِيًّۭا مِّنَ ٱلصَّٰلِحِينَ","translationText":"And We gave him good tidings of Isaac, a prophet from among the righteous."},{"key":"37:113","surahNumber":37,"ayahNumber":113,"juzNumber":23,"pageNumber":450,"arabicText":"وَبَٰرَكْنَا عَلَيْهِ وَعَلَىٰٓ إِسْحَٰقَ ۚ وَمِن ذُرِّيَّتِهِمَا مُحْسِنٌۭ وَظَالِمٌۭ لِّنَفْسِهِۦ مُبِينٌۭ","translationText":"And We blessed him and Isaac. But among their descendants is the doer of good and the clearly unjust to himself."},{"key":"37:114","surahNumber":37,"ayahNumber":114,"juzNumber":23,"pageNumber":450,"arabicText":"وَلَقَدْ مَنَنَّا عَلَىٰ مُوسَىٰ وَهَٰرُونَ","translationText":"And We did certainly confer favor upon Moses and Aaron."},{"key":"37:115","surahNumber":37,"ayahNumber":115,"juzNumber":23,"pageNumber":450,"arabicText":"وَنَجَّيْنَٰهُمَا وَقَوْمَهُمَا مِنَ ٱلْكَرْبِ ٱلْعَظِيمِ","translationText":"And We saved them and their people from the great affliction,"},{"key":"37:116","surahNumber":37,"ayahNumber":116,"juzNumber":23,"pageNumber":450,"arabicText":"وَنَصَرْنَٰهُمْ فَكَانُوا۟ هُمُ ٱلْغَٰلِبِينَ","translationText":"And We supported them so it was they who overcame."},{"key":"37:117","surahNumber":37,"ayahNumber":117,"juzNumber":23,"pageNumber":450,"arabicText":"وَءَاتَيْنَٰهُمَا ٱلْكِتَٰبَ ٱلْمُسْتَبِينَ","translationText":"And We gave them the explicit Scripture,"},{"key":"37:118","surahNumber":37,"ayahNumber":118,"juzNumber":23,"pageNumber":450,"arabicText":"وَهَدَيْنَٰهُمَا ٱلصِّرَٰطَ ٱلْمُسْتَقِيمَ","translationText":"And We guided them on the straight path."},{"key":"37:119","surahNumber":37,"ayahNumber":119,"juzNumber":23,"pageNumber":450,"arabicText":"وَتَرَكْنَا عَلَيْهِمَا فِى ٱلْءَاخِرِينَ","translationText":"And We left for them [favorable mention] among later generations:"},{"key":"37:120","surahNumber":37,"ayahNumber":120,"juzNumber":23,"pageNumber":450,"arabicText":"سَلَٰمٌ عَلَىٰ مُوسَىٰ وَهَٰرُونَ","translationText":"\"Peace upon Moses and Aaron.\""},{"key":"37:121","surahNumber":37,"ayahNumber":121,"juzNumber":23,"pageNumber":450,"arabicText":"إِنَّا كَذَٰلِكَ نَجْزِى ٱلْمُحْسِنِينَ","translationText":"Indeed, We thus reward the doers of good."},{"key":"37:122","surahNumber":37,"ayahNumber":122,"juzNumber":23,"pageNumber":450,"arabicText":"إِنَّهُمَا مِنْ عِبَادِنَا ٱلْمُؤْمِنِينَ","translationText":"Indeed, they were of Our believing servants."},{"key":"37:123","surahNumber":37,"ayahNumber":123,"juzNumber":23,"pageNumber":450,"arabicText":"وَإِنَّ إِلْيَاسَ لَمِنَ ٱلْمُرْسَلِينَ","translationText":"And indeed, Elias was from among the messengers,"},{"key":"37:124","surahNumber":37,"ayahNumber":124,"juzNumber":23,"pageNumber":450,"arabicText":"إِذْ قَالَ لِقَوْمِهِۦٓ أَلَا تَتَّقُونَ","translationText":"When he said to his people, \"Will you not fear Allah?"},{"key":"37:125","surahNumber":37,"ayahNumber":125,"juzNumber":23,"pageNumber":450,"arabicText":"أَتَدْعُونَ بَعْلًۭا وَتَذَرُونَ أَحْسَنَ ٱلْخَٰلِقِينَ","translationText":"Do you call upon Ba'l and leave the best of creators -"},{"key":"37:126","surahNumber":37,"ayahNumber":126,"juzNumber":23,"pageNumber":450,"arabicText":"ٱللَّهَ رَبَّكُمْ وَرَبَّ ءَابَآئِكُمُ ٱلْأَوَّلِينَ","translationText":"Allah, your Lord and the Lord of your first forefathers?\""}],"translationEditionUsed":"en.sahih"}